    {
      "id": "tutorial-archive-overview",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Overview",
      "position": {
        "x": -420,
        "y": -700
      },
      "width": 700,
      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "identity": {
          "graphId": "tutorial-archive"
        },
        "markdown": "# Tutorial Archive\n\nThis graph indexes tutorial content moved out of `twilite/public/tutorial` and into `twilite-zone/public/tutorial/archive/legacy-public-tutorial`.\n\nUse this as a holding shelf while we decide what deserves repair, migration, or deletion.\n\nThe archive keeps the original files available without leaving them mixed into the live tutorial surface."
      }
    },
